headline: Smurfit Westrock announces permanent closure of a paper machine at La Tuque mill
summary: DUBLIN, February 10, 2026-- Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE: SW, LSE: SWR) today announced it will permanently close one of the paper machines at its La Tuque, Quebec, mill. The machine’s annual production capacity of 127,000 tons of solid bleached sulfate (SBS) has faced ongoing scale and cost challenges.
